1
00:00:00,427 --> 00:00:01,865
<i>Previously on</i> Jericho

2
00:00:02,536 --> 00:00:03,542
Hello, Jonah.

3
00:00:03,642 --> 00:00:06,258
Guy did four years at Lansing
for extortion and assault.

4
00:00:06,383 --> 00:00:07,545
Why are you talking to him?

5
00:00:07,645 --> 00:00:10,125
It's okay, all right?
It didn't have anything to do with you.

6
00:00:10,235 --> 00:00:13,254
He's my father...
it has everything to do with me.

7
00:00:13,354 --> 00:00:16,864
Jonah agrees to leave town
and not come back.

8
00:00:16,964 --> 00:00:17,965
Exile.

9
00:00:18,065 --> 00:00:19,723
Johnston, you SOB.

10
00:00:19,895 --> 00:00:21,456
How the hell did you lose an election?

11
00:00:21,556 --> 00:00:24,178
No, the question is how did you get
to be in charge of New Bern?

12
00:00:24,278 --> 00:00:25,930
They get tired of you
being the sheriff?

13
00:00:26,047 --> 00:00:28,385
No, I m still sheriff.
Just got a little more authority.

14
00:00:28,485 --> 00:00:30,438
Does this thing work?
Can we get power from it?

15
00:00:30,507 --> 00:00:31,599
Probably sometime tomorrow.

16
00:00:31,685 --> 00:00:33,251
All right, let's get it up
as fast as we can.

17
00:00:33,351 --> 00:00:34,534
Can we bust some more
of these things?

18
00:00:34,634 --> 00:00:37,197
You got one of the only salt mines
around for 400 miles.

19
00:00:37,303 --> 00:00:38,312
We're going to need food.

20
00:00:38,412 --> 00:00:40,325
Ten wind turbines for, let's say...

21
00:00:40,517 --> 00:00:41,812
ten percent of your spring crop.

22
00:00:41,921 --> 00:00:43,679
Okay, look, we'll give you the food.

23
00:00:43,779 --> 00:00:46,341
We're going to need ten Jericho men
to help us build them.

24
00:00:46,786 --> 00:00:48,678
I didn't know you guys
were coming back today.

25
00:00:48,766 --> 00:00:50,211
It wasn't safe for us there anymore.

26
00:00:50,264 --> 00:00:52,694
- Where's my brother?
- He hasn't been seen for a few days.

27
00:00:52,794 --> 00:00:55,777
You can't just ride into New Bern
and start breaking china.

28
00:00:56,304 --> 00:00:58,405
It's a full inventory of Jericho.

29
00:00:58,505 --> 00:01:00,228
They sliced it up like they own it.

30
00:01:00,328 --> 00:01:01,824
They're making mortar rounds.

31
00:01:01,924 --> 00:01:03,325
They're getting ready for war.

32
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,443
Hold it!

33
00:01:04,543 --> 00:01:06,396
There was going to be
an explosion in town.

34
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:09,419
Hopefully, we can somehow
get Jake and Eric out of there.

35
00:01:17,348 --> 00:01:18,368
Everybody, go!

36
00:01:31,562 --> 00:01:33,241
All right, keep alert.
Jake said the New Bern guys

37
00:01:33,288 --> 00:01:34,862
might be coming right behind them.

38
00:01:37,511 --> 00:01:39,002
Maybe they're already here.

39
00:01:43,289 --> 00:01:44,290
What is that?

40
00:01:58,709 --> 00:01:59,711
What happened?

41
00:02:00,274 --> 00:02:01,870
We got a major problem, Gray.

42
00:02:03,716 --> 00:02:04,717
Where's Eric?

43
00:02:04,842 --> 00:02:07,173
He's fine.
He's at the med center.

44
00:02:10,545 --> 00:02:12,063
Well, is it about the mine?

45
00:02:14,394 --> 00:02:15,896
It's a lot worse than that.

46
00:02:27,132 --> 00:02:28,142
Who are you?

47
00:02:31,508 --> 00:02:32,932
Stop moving.

48
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,311
You hear me?

49
00:02:37,015 --> 00:02:38,063
I'm talking to you.

50
00:02:38,595 --> 00:02:39,596
Freeze!

51
00:02:55,448 --> 00:02:56,653
Who are you?

52
00:03:00,502 --> 00:03:01,832
I think we killed...

53
00:03:02,511 --> 00:03:04,107
six in New Bern.

54
00:03:06,907 --> 00:03:07,971
I counted eight.

55
00:03:19,024 --> 00:03:20,026
Who's this?

56
00:03:20,761 --> 00:03:22,096
Says he's from New Bern.

57
00:03:22,597 --> 00:03:23,817
Wanted to talk to you.

58
00:03:24,255 --> 00:03:25,304
What is this about?

59
00:03:47,367 --> 00:03:49,370
<i>Am I speaking to Gray Anderson?

60
00:03:53,272 --> 00:03:54,930
<i>This is Phil Constantino.

61
00:03:57,809 --> 00:04:00,078
<i>Henry, you can
come home now, son.

62
00:04:04,797 --> 00:04:06,768
<i>We're still cleaning the blood
of eight deputies

63
00:04:06,868 --> 00:04:08,476
<i>off the sidewalks of New Bern,

64
00:04:09,618 --> 00:04:11,668
<i>so you need to understand
our position.

65
00:04:14,128 --> 00:04:15,458
<i>We need seven farms,

66
00:04:15,755 --> 00:04:17,555
<i>including the Jackson farm,

67
00:04:17,664 --> 00:04:18,791
<i>the Herbert farm,

68
00:04:19,010 --> 00:04:20,480
<i>and the Richmond farm.

69
00:04:21,982 --> 00:04:23,911
And we need half the salt mine.

70
00:04:24,339 --> 00:04:26,274
You have four hours to respond.

71
00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:30,075
I don't understand.
What are you asking us to do?

72
00:04:31,064 --> 00:04:33,176
Jericho is about to be invaded.

73
00:04:33,661 --> 00:04:35,226
For the sake of your people,

74
00:04:35,523 --> 00:04:36,915
I'm asking you...

75
00:04:37,197 --> 00:04:38,276
to surrender.

76
